    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total dream on wheels? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in pristine shape! This car has been lovingly cared for and looks just as good as the day it rolled off the lot. It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road with a new owner who will appreciate it as much as I have. You seriously won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
