    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this beauty. Honestly, it's in such incredible shape that it still feels brand new! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and kept totally spotless. It drives like a absolute dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m so sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all, I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
