      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with a flawlessly maintained double-VANOS system and crisp individual throttle bodies. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and delivered through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and retains its original suspension geometry with no bushing deflection. The exterior finish is concours-ready, and the interior is pristine, showing zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster. A turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the purist driver.",
